NIKO SEMICONDUCT said unconsolidated sales
in April fell 41.21% to NT$232,136,000 from NT$394,855,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  4/2012           4/2011
Sales            232,136          394,855    
YOY%             -41.21%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales            844,534         1,290,478   
YOY%             -34.56% 
=================================================================
 